These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, camping, card-games, caring
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, photographer, scientist, writer
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, house, r&b, trance
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, car, helicopter, bus
1. the photographer is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
2. the fan of trance is on the left of the person driving the car##1
3. the fan of r&b is the designer##1
4. the person who's hobby is caring is on the right of the photographer##1
5. the scientist is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
6. the fan of country is on the left of the fan of house##1
7. the photographer is the person driving the trike##1
8. the fan of house is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
9. the person who's hobby is caring is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | board-games  | caring  | camping | card-games |
| Job           | photographer | designer | writer  | scientist  |
| Music-Genre   | trance       | r&b      | country | house      |
| Transport           | trike          | car     | helicopter    | bus     |

