3. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
4. the electrician is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
5. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
6. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
7. the freelancer is the person driving the bus##1
8. the person driving the scooter is the person traveling to paris##1
9. the person driving the skateboard is the person traveling to colone##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |      3      |     4      |
| City      | prague      | paris         | edinburgh        | colone      |
| Job           | freelancer | electrician | journalist  | paramedic  |
| Movie-Genre   | western    | musical     | time-travel | zombie     |
| Transport     | bus        | scooter     | jet-ski     | skateboard |

